# React-Portfolio
Created a Portfolio using React 

# Description 
[![forthebadge](https://forthebadge.com/images/badges/built-with-grammas-recipe.svg)](https://forthebadge.com)
[![forthebadge](https://forthebadge.com/images/badges/built-with-love.svg)](https://forthebadge.com)


Built this project/Portfolio with React. It contains a simple home page that can navigate to Projects, About, and Contact Page. 
I styled the pages using [![forthebadge](data:image/svg+xml;base64,)](https://forthebadge.com) . The footer contains links to my LinkedIn , Github, and Twitter accounts. 


 ## ðŸ›  Installation and Setup Instructions

1. Installation: `npm install`

2. In the project directory, you can run: `npm start`

Runs the app in the development mode.\
Open [http://localhost:3000](http://localhost:3000) to view it in the browser.
The page will reload if you make edits.
